137
00:10:18,700 --> 00:10:19,620
We will.

138
00:10:19,620 --> 00:10:21,270
This is for you. Please take it.

139
00:10:21,670 --> 00:10:23,500
All right. Thanks.

140
00:10:26,340 --> 00:10:27,740
Be careful with the equipment.

141
00:10:29,310 --> 00:10:30,580
Take it easy.

142
00:10:31,390 --> 00:10:32,190
Thank you.

143
00:10:32,620 --> 00:10:33,430
Thanks.

144
00:10:39,550 --> 00:10:40,220
Director Dai!

145
00:10:41,670 --> 00:10:42,860
Heard you're making a film.

146
00:10:43,160 --> 00:10:44,590
(Such A Good Love!)
Any part for me?

147
00:10:46,620 --> 00:10:47,430
Ze?

148
00:10:51,190 --> 00:10:53,460
Any parts for us?

149
00:10:54,220 --> 00:10:55,340
Hope you didn't forget us.

150
00:10:58,910 --> 00:10:59,700
Xiaomao.

151
00:11:00,950 --> 00:11:01,740
Xue Cheng.

152
00:11:02,500 --> 00:11:03,220
You guys...

