155
00:12:00,300 --> 00:12:02,420
(Demolish)

156
00:12:04,430 --> 00:12:05,860
They're tearing this place down.

157
00:12:06,100 --> 00:12:07,190
Can we still film here?

158
00:12:07,430 --> 00:12:08,620
We can. I checked.

159
00:12:08,620 --> 00:12:10,100
The demolition will start in a week.

160
00:12:10,100 --> 00:12:11,620
As long as we move fast,

161
00:12:11,620 --> 00:12:12,500
