162
00:12:14,150 --> 00:12:15,740
Where is this place?

163
00:12:17,220 --> 00:12:18,860
Why do we have to shoot here?

164
00:12:20,150 --> 00:12:21,430
This place is called

165
00:12:22,500 --> 00:12:23,580
Chunzhili Residence.

166
00:12:25,460 --> 00:12:26,950
Chunzhili Residence.

167
00:12:29,910 --> 00:12:30,860
Are we good to go?

168
00:12:30,860 --> 00:12:31,620
Yes. Let's roll.

169
00:12:31,620 --> 00:12:32,270
Okay.

170
00:12:33,220 --> 00:12:36,500
Scene 28, shot 7, take 1.
Three, two, one.

171
00:12:36,670 --> 00:12:37,460
Action!

172
00:12:46,550 --> 00:12:48,100
Xue Cheng, tilt a little to the left.

173
00:12:49,500 --> 00:12:51,190
Hey! Who are you people?

174
00:12:51,740 --> 00:12:52,550
What are you doing?

175
00:12:52,550 --> 00:12:54,430
- We're shooting a film.
- Sir...

176
00:12:54,430 --> 00:12:55,030
Sorry, sir.

177
00:12:55,030 --> 00:12:56,430
We're filming here.

178
00:12:56,580 --> 00:12:57,390
Filming what?

179
00:12:58,190 --> 00:12:58,980
Sir.

180
00:12:59,270 --> 00:13:01,310
We're just making a film.

181
00:13:02,740 --> 00:13:04,670
What film?

182
00:13:04,740 --> 00:13:06,670
Don't you know
this place is getting demolished?

183
00:13:06,670 --> 00:13:07,430
We do.

184
00:13:08,270 --> 00:13:09,550
Pack up and get out.

185
00:13:10,100 --> 00:13:12,150
Sir, you're in charge here, right?

186
00:13:12,950 --> 00:13:13,790
Cigarette.

187
00:13:14,190 --> 00:13:14,950
I'm sorry.

188
00:13:14,950 --> 00:13:16,700
Very sorry for the delay.

189
00:13:16,860 --> 00:13:18,620
We won't take long.

190
00:13:18,740 --> 00:13:20,430
We'll wrap up quickly.
Won't hold you up.

191
00:13:20,430 --> 00:13:21,190
Or maybe

192
00:13:21,190 --> 00:13:23,950
I could pay a small location fee?

193
00:13:24,500 --> 00:13:25,310
Have a cigarette.

194
00:13:26,740 --> 00:13:27,950
Forget it!

195
00:13:28,620 --> 00:13:29,430
Miss.

196
00:13:31,910 --> 00:13:35,430
I'm in charge of the entire site.

197
00:13:35,500 --> 00:13:38,430
You think I need your pocket change?

198
00:13:40,100 --> 00:13:41,030
Clear them out.

199
00:13:41,030 --> 00:13:43,190
Tear down all this junk.

200
00:13:43,190 --> 00:13:43,950
On it, Mr. Zhang.

201
00:13:43,950 --> 00:13:45,550
You guys, clean this place up.

202
00:13:46,150 --> 00:13:47,860
Sir, we can wrap this up in no time!

203
00:13:48,150 --> 00:13:48,950
Don't touch that!

204
00:13:48,950 --> 00:13:49,430
Move it!

205
00:13:49,700 --> 00:13:50,550
No, wait! Actors!

206
00:13:50,550 --> 00:13:51,820
Get out of there! Move!

207
00:13:51,820 --> 00:13:52,500
Xiaomao! Move!

208
00:13:52,500 --> 00:13:53,700
Come here! Don't fight them!

209
00:13:53,720 --> 00:13:54,580
Darn it.

210
00:13:54,580 --> 00:13:55,670
I'll go talk to him.

211
00:13:55,820 --> 00:13:57,430
What's there to talk about?

212
00:13:57,430 --> 00:13:58,620
They're just a bunch of thugs.

213
00:13:58,620 --> 00:13:59,500
Yes. Let's go

214
00:13:59,500 --> 00:14:00,230
to somewhere else.

215
00:14:00,230 --> 00:14:01,190
Agreed.

216
00:14:01,190 --> 00:14:02,150
I'll help you find one.

217
00:14:02,150 --> 00:14:02,550
No.

218
00:14:03,220 --> 00:14:04,620
This film has to be shot here.

219
00:14:11,430 --> 00:14:12,620
This way. Over here.

220
00:14:12,790 --> 00:14:13,580
Mr. Zhang!

221
00:14:15,100 --> 00:14:16,670
You're Mr. Zhang, right?

222
00:14:17,310 --> 00:14:19,270
Can we talk for a minute?

223
00:14:19,340 --> 00:14:20,910
Just give us time

224
00:14:21,310 --> 00:14:22,270
to finish

225
00:14:22,270 --> 00:14:23,950
the scene over there.

226
00:14:24,340 --> 00:14:25,070
Just one day.

227
00:14:25,070 --> 00:14:26,910
I promise we'll finish in a day.

228
00:14:26,910 --> 00:14:28,270
Then you can tear it all down.

229
00:14:29,670 --> 00:14:30,740
Not a chance.

230
00:14:30,860 --> 00:14:32,620
Didn't you see we've already started?

231
00:14:32,740 --> 00:14:33,980
The excavators are already here.

232
00:14:33,980 --> 00:14:35,030
Then tear this side first.

233
00:14:35,030 --> 00:14:36,100
Just give me that side.

234
00:14:36,100 --> 00:14:37,390
I'll finish in one day,

235
00:14:37,390 --> 00:14:38,340
then we'll leave.

236
00:14:38,340 --> 00:14:39,620
We won't delay anything, okay?

237
00:14:39,820 --> 00:14:41,620
Besides, your notice says demolition

238
00:14:41,620 --> 00:14:42,950
starts next week.

239
00:14:42,950 --> 00:14:44,550
It also said, "may start early."

240
00:14:44,740 --> 00:14:45,670
Wait, Mr. Zhang...

241
00:14:45,740 --> 00:14:46,580
I'm begging you.

242
00:14:46,580 --> 00:14:47,550
This is really important.

243
00:14:47,550 --> 00:14:49,070
I have to finish this shoot today.

244
00:14:49,070 --> 00:14:49,770
One day. I swear.

245
00:14:49,770 --> 00:14:51,150
Listen. Just leave now.

246
00:14:52,270 --> 00:14:53,190
If you don't leave now,

247
00:14:53,430 --> 00:14:55,500
I'll tear down this whole street
with you in it.

248
00:14:59,190 --> 00:15:01,190
If you don't let me shoot today,

249
00:15:01,670 --> 00:15:03,100
you are tearing nothing down!

250
00:15:10,430 --> 00:15:11,550
Just ignore her.

251
00:15:11,550 --> 00:15:12,950
All right. Rotate this way. Come on.

252
00:15:12,950 --> 00:15:14,580
Don't tear it down! Stop!

253
00:15:14,740 --> 00:15:15,550
Out of my way!

254
00:15:15,700 --> 00:15:18,340
Come on! Dig into me then!

255
00:15:19,220 --> 00:15:20,340
Go on, tear me down with it!

256
00:15:21,950 --> 00:15:23,500
Then maybe...

257
00:15:23,500 --> 00:15:24,460
Tear that side first.

258
00:15:24,460 --> 00:15:25,430
Over there.

259
00:15:25,570 --> 00:15:26,620
- Right here.
- Come on.

260
00:15:26,620 --> 00:15:29,030
No! Not here either!

261
00:15:29,700 --> 00:15:30,980
No one's tearing anything down!

262
00:15:42,690 --> 00:15:43,580
Are you leaving or not?

263
00:15:45,860 --> 00:15:47,340
Just give me one day!

264
00:15:47,340 --> 00:15:49,150
You want me to smash your face?

265
00:15:49,500 --> 00:15:50,820
Just one day!

266
00:15:51,740 --> 00:15:52,860
Please...

267
00:16:02,740 --> 00:16:04,270
Are you insane or something?

268
00:16:06,150 --> 00:16:07,860
Just treat me like I'm crazy then.

269
00:16:08,500 --> 00:16:10,220
Just let me film for one day.

270
00:16:11,030 --> 00:16:12,620
- Take her away.
- Come on.

271
00:16:12,620 --> 00:16:13,700
You...

272
00:16:14,550 --> 00:16:16,460
Let me go!

273
00:16:23,580 --> 00:16:25,100
I'll be standing right here!

274
00:16:25,310 --> 00:16:26,610
Tear it down with me if you dare!

275
00:16:27,860 --> 00:16:28,390
Fine.

276
00:16:30,950 --> 00:16:31,740
Looks like

277
00:16:31,820 --> 00:16:34,270
dust is everywhere at this site.

278
00:16:35,550 --> 00:16:37,860
Bring the water truck over.
Spray it down.

279
00:16:51,860 --> 00:16:52,740
You leaving now?

280
00:16:52,950 --> 00:16:53,740
No!

281
00:16:57,500 --> 00:16:57,980
Spray her.

282
00:17:05,950 --> 00:17:06,740
Nice and cold!

283
00:17:16,830 --> 00:17:18,020
You leaving now?

284
00:17:19,430 --> 00:17:20,220
Still not leaving!

